====Usage notes====
{{lang|mul|行}} itself is also used as a radical (in addition to {{l|mul|彳}}); unusually for radicals, the phonetic is placed in the ''middle'' – with {{lang|mul|彳}} on the left and {{lang|mul|亍}} on the right – corresponding to the phonetic originally being placed at the middle of the intersection.

